Edits, additions and deletions welcome.

md style guide:

- Don't exceed 80 char width
- One sentence per line, if needed you can subdivide at commas, phrases, etc.
- If you want a paragraph don't include an extra new line.
- Except for sentences in paragraphs, you must include and extra new line.
- Spellcheck before committing changes, locale 'en_us'.
- All sentences must end in punctuation mark except for headers.
- For headers use proper title capitalization.
